name: #3B - Zhúfù - Self
description:
#3B - Zhúfù - Peace  - Zhúfù translates to blessing in Chinese. The series will be broken into 5 sub-blessings.

Self -  Self -  The inner self, it can be a place of solice or deep sense of darkness. This piece represents of a way to acknowledge pain, but even in the dark there is always light. One just might have to look further than one's own way. 

You can find more on Twitter @generatecoll or Instagram @generate.collective (2021)

Size: 4000x4000 px
